premise_source_doc_sentence: Yang Hyun-suk  (  born December 2 , 1969  )  is a South Korean music executive , rapper , dancer and record producer .
He rose to fame as a member of Seo Taiji and Boys during the 1990s .
After the group disbanded , he founded and became chief executive officer of YG Entertainment , one of the biggest record companies in South Korea .

Akdong Musician  (  악동뮤지션 , also known as AKMU  )  is a South Korean duo who participated on K-pop Star 2 in 2012 and debuted under YG Entertainment in 2014 after they won the second installment of the K-pop Star series .

This is a list of awards and nominations received by Akdong Musician , a South Korean duo who participated on K-pop Star 2 in 2012 and debuted under YG Entertainment in 2014 after they won the second installment of the K-pop Star series .

The original three judges for the series were Yang Hyun-suk , founder of YG Entertainment and former member of the popular South Korean act Seo Taiji & Boys , Park Jin-young , singer/songwriter and founder of JYP Entertainment , and Korean pop icon BoA , from SM Entertainment .
Yang Hyun-suk , Park Jin-young , and You Hee-yeol will return as judges .
